      "content": "thanks. i checked the receiving logs and they look perfect, and shipping matches up too. it's like the units are just... disappearing during the processing phase. it's not a large enough number to look like theft, but it's constant. any other ideas for why we'd see this kind of unexplained, small-scale loss?",
